{
  "text": "Sea trout were caught in sweep nets at sea at various locations on the west coast of Scotland primarily during the May to July period in 1997 to 2015. See [CITATION_1] for a detailed description of the sampling strategy.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "294555"
